@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@contentType = application/json
@adminToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.data.token}}
@userToken = {{loginUser.response.body.data.token}}

### Prerequisites: Run auth.rest first to get tokens

### 1. Get Dashboard Stats (Positive Case - Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2. Get Stats (Negative Case - Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats

### 3. Get Stats (Negative Case - Forbidden - Normal User)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
